{"tid":492963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母01又幫水貨佬洗底","createTime":"2017-12-08T05:07:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T12:32:18.000Z","uid":64056,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c827a71a4e01eecd32c491ca5096ae2f1b441f35","tid":492963,"uid":64056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:07:40.000Z","msg":"90後水貨客自白<br />\n「走私小隊」品流複雜卻無分貴賤：大家只是求生<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Joseph一直是個循規蹈矩的學生，而且文靜，極其量只是內心有種對另類文化的渴望。從前不會覺得自己會接觸到社會這一面。「最初會覺得幾mindfucked，最深刻的是一對有智障的情侶；一個大肚婆拖著媽媽，二人都似是受毒品所害，走在身旁走貨。會覺得這個社會為什麼會這樣。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80/138708/90%E5%BE%8C%E6%B0%B4%E8%B2%A8%E5%AE%A2%E8%87%AA%E7%99%BD-%E8%B5%B0%E7%A7%81%E5%B0%8F%E9%9A%8A-%E5%93%81%E6%B5%81%E8%A4%87%E9%9B%9C%E5%8D%BB%E7%84%A1%E5%88%86%E8%B2%B4%E8%B3%A4-%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6%E5%8F%AA%E6%98%AF%E6%B1%82%E7%94%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%258D%2580%2F138708%2F90%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E8%25B2%25A8%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2599%25BD-%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E7%25A7%2581%25E5%25B0%258F%25E9%259A%258A-%25E5%2593%2581%25E6%25B5%2581%25E8%25A4%2587%25E9%259B%259C%25E5%258D%25BB%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%2588%2586%25E8%25B2%25B4%25E8%25B3%25A4-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%258F%25AA%25E6%2598%25AF%25E6%25B1%2582%25E7%2594%259F&d=jDd7n1Vz9sOp%2FOQjG5TxkROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=47900d2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80/138708/90%E5%BE%8C%E6%B0%B4%E8%B2%A8%E5%AE%A2%E8%87%AA%E7%99%BD-%E8%B5%B0%E7%A7%81%E5%B0%8F%E9%9A%8A-%E5%93%81%E6%B5%81%E8%A4%87%E9%9B%9C%E5%8D%BB%E7%84%A1%E5%88%86%E8%B2%B4%E8%B3%A4-%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6%E5%8F%AA%E6%98%AF%E6%B1%82%E7%94%9F</a><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母水貨狗<br />\n走水貨走到大義懍然咁撚樣<br />\n有哂人生體會<br />\n只係平民百姓撚體諒佢地咁<br />\n仆街啦hk01、水貨狗"},{"pid":"bb1c070ff02f89d5e3667717815fada163d97bee","tid":492963,"uid":64056,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:14:44.000Z","msg":"01同東張西望d套路一樣<br />\n一開始就出報道<br />\n講而家香港面對緊一個社會問題 (水貨問題)<br />\n屌柒政府、各公營機構辦事不力，導致民怨四起<br />\n好似好撚為民請命咁<br />\n<br />\n隔一排又出個報導<br />\n整個人物專訪<br />\n訪問下d當事人 (水貨狗)<br />\n講到當事人好似好委屈<br />\n社會唔明白佢咁<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d1202b4efba47497c17c80fc0b6b5d3f55ab690","tid":492963,"uid":151700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:22:35.000Z","msg":"其實原本都keep住有人提支那01好紅底成日文中加插紅底既野<br />\n<br />\n點知仲係咁多人睇都唔知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b5941d77ee6246c82492d02c40414853ed84044","tid":492963,"uid":86841,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:26:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"78b181523eadc15ca562e4b944af0c12cc73786c","tid":492963,"uid":77143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:28:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>走水貨同香港人炒賣股票/樓一樣，靠食差價維生，唔明呢度d on9做咩屌水貨客</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 炒股票有交印花稅咖<br />\n水貨客有無交稅啊"},{"pid":"728ac863e60828d3e4bfcb15a1a3e29373444972","tid":492963,"uid":86841,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:29:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"afd73cfab99879a6aee084acfd0057b288b9a950","tid":492963,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:30:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實原本都keep住有人提支那01好紅底成日文中加插紅底既野<br />\n<br />\n點知仲係咁多人睇都唔知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連登不嬲多小學雞,轉個頭唔記得"},{"pid":"204b585bc3f3df4ea500c2f811f55e5011e842ed","tid":492963,"uid":77143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:58:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>走水貨同香港人炒賣股票/樓一樣，靠食差價維生，唔明呢度d on9做咩屌水貨客</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/asset